HEADWORD: Nosesmart
<hw>Nose"smart`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A kind of cress, a pungent cruciferous plant, including several
species of the genus <gen>Nasturtium</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

